# AST environment and type resolution

Sorted shells become semantic identities and visibility.

## Contract

- Input: sorted declaration headers and header-built visibility
- Output: populated `TypeEnvironment`, resolved signatures and `ScopeContext`
- Decides: type identity, generic instances, public facade API, member lookup
- Must not decide: body expression semantics, HIR control flow, backend lowering
- Invariant: `TypeId` equality in the active environment is the only semantic comparison rule

## Main paths

- `src/compiler_frontend/ast/module_ast/environment/`
- `src/compiler_frontend/ast/type_resolution/`
- `src/compiler_frontend/datatypes/`

